===============================================================================
[ Examples ]

Example #1 A runkit_function_add() example

<?php >
  runkit_function_add('testme','$a,$b','echo "The value of a is $a\n";
   echo "The value of b is $b\n";');
  testme(1,2);
<?>

The above example will output:

The value of a is 1
The value of b is 2

